# STM32CubeMX .ioc 配置文件
# 将此文件保存为 SmartWatch.ioc，用 CubeMX 打开即可生成完整工程
#
# 手动配置步骤（如无法直接打开 .ioc，按以下设置）:

# ===== 芯片选择 =====
# PartNumber: STM32F103C8Tx

# ===== RCC =====
# HSE: Crystal/Ceramic Resonator
# LSE: Disabled

# ===== SYS =====
# Timebase Source: TIM1
# Debug: Serial Wire

# ===== I2C1 =====
# Mode: I2C
# PB6: I2C1_SCL
# PB7: I2C1_SDA
# Parameter: Speed Mode = Standard (100KHz)

# ===== USART1 (Optional) =====
# Mode: Asynchronous
# PA9: USART1_TX
# PA10: USART1_RX
# Parameter: Baud Rate = 9600

# ===== GPIO =====
# PA0: GPIO_EXTI0, GPIO mode = External Interrupt Mode with Falling edge trigger detection
#        GPIO Pull-up/Pull-down = Pull-up
# PA2: GPIO_Output, Output level = Low

# ===== TIM2 =====
# Clock Source: Internal Clock
# Prescaler: 7200-1
# Counter Period: 10000-1
# Auto-reload preload: Enable
# NVIC Settings: TIM2 global interrupt = Enabled

# ===== NVIC =====
# EXTI line0 interrupt: Enabled, Preemption=5, Sub=0
# TIM2 global interrupt: Enabled, Preemption=5, Sub=0

# ===== FreeRTOS =====
# Interface: CMSIS_V2
# Memory Management: heap_4

# ===== Clock Configuration =====
# HSE: 8MHz
# PLL Source: HSE
# PLL Mul: x9
# System Clock: 72MHz
# APB1 Prescaler: /2 (36MHz)
# APB2 Prescaler: /1 (72MHz)
# Flash Latency: 2

# ===== Project Settings =====
# Project Name: SmartWatch
# Toolchain/IDE: MDK-ARM (或 STM32CubeIDE)
# Generate peripheral initialization as a pair of .c/.h files per peripheral: ✓
